---
import { TypingAnimation } from "./TypingAnimation";
---

<section id="why">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-screen-xl flex-col gap-8 px-4 py-14 md:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl text-center">
      <TypingAnimation
        client:visible
        className="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl"
        text="<¿Por qué participar?/>"
      />
    </div>

    <div
      class="mx-auto max-w-4xl grid w-full justify-center items-center md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-4 md:mt-8"
    >
      <div class="max-w-[400px] flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mx-auto">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="text-brand2 w-20 h-20"
          ><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="1"></circle><path d="m9 20 3-6 3 6"
          ></path><path d="m6 8 6 2 6-2"></path><path d="M12 10v4"></path></svg
        >

        <p class="text-lg">Aprende de expertos en IA y sostenibilidad</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-[400px] flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mx-auto">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="text-brand2 w-20 h-20"
          ><path d="M6 9H4.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H6"></path><path
            d="M18 9h1.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 0-5H18"></path><path d="M4 22h16"
          ></path><path
            d="M10 14.66V17c0 .55-.47.98-.97 1.21C7.85 18.75 7 20.24 7 22"
          ></path><path
            d="M14 14.66V17c0 .55.47.98.97 1.21C16.15 18.75 17 20.24 17 22"
          ></path><path d="M18 2H6v7a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2Z"></path></svg
        >

        <p class="text-lg">Compite por premios emocionantes</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-[400px] flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mx-auto">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="text-brand2 w-20 h-20"
          ><path d="M16 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle
            cx="9"
            cy="7"
            r="4"></circle><path d="M22 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path
            d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg
        >

        <p class="text-lg">Conéctate con otros innovadores</p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-[400px] flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mx-auto">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          class="text-brand2 w-20 h-20"
          ><path d="M7 10v12"></path><path
            d="M15 5.88 14 10h5.83a2 2 0 0 1 1.92 2.56l-2.33 8A2 2 0 0 1 17.5 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2.76a2 2 0 0 0 1.79-1.11L12 2a3.13 3.13 0 0 1 3 3.88Z"
          ></path></svg
        >

        <p class="text-lg">¡Haz una diferencia en el mundo!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
